org.opensha2.eq.fault.scaling

Class MagLengthRelationship

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opensha2.eq.fault.scaling.MagScalingRelationship
      • org.opensha2.eq.fault.scaling.MagLengthRelationship
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Named
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GeoMat_MagLenthRelationship, WC1994_MagLengthRelationship

    public abstract class MagLengthRelationship
extends MagScalingRelationship
    This is an abstract class that gives the median and standard deviation of magnitude as a function of length (km) or visa versa. The values can also be a function of rake. Note that the standard deviation for length as a function of mag is given for natural-log(length) not length.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Edward H. Field
